React day 2 Daily Revision

1."Vite la public folder index.html la iruka div id="root" ku React main.jsx mooliyama connect pannum. Athu la mattum thaan namma functional components (App, Home, Navbar…) ellam render aagum."



2.src la iruka ReactDOM.createRoot() function thaan 
React-oda Virtual DOM rendering process-a start pannum.

Virtual DOM-na, browser-la already iruka Real DOM structure-oda 
oru lightweight copy React memory-la create pannum.

Enga update nadakutho, antha specific DOM part mattum thaan 
re-render aagum. Whole page re-render aagathu. 
Adhanala React fast & efficient-aa work pannum.

ReactDOM.createRoot → Virtual DOM use pannuradhu

ReactDOM.createRoot() nu solradhu React 18+ introduced method.
Idhu React UI-a mount panna (attach panna) and Virtual DOM engine-a initialize panna use aagum.




